        "The bulletin's 'Major Electives' rule says 'two additional PHIL-UA courses, except introductory courses (which are numbered 1 through 8)'. Phase 7-A P-2 added `excludeFromPool` to the rule schema; this rule now correctly excludes PHIL-UA 1-8 from the elective pool. Per the bulletin Note (line 162), students may only take ONE intro course anyway, so a student can satisfy the intro requirement and the elective requirement without ambiguity.",
